query:
SELECT 
                    id,
                    signature,
                    collection_id,
                    payer,
                    data_service,
                    service_provider,
                    timestamp_ns,
                    nonce,
                    value
                FROM tap_horizon_receipts
                WHERE
                    collection_id = $1
                    AND payer = $2
                    AND service_provider = $3
                    AND signer_address IN (SELECT unnest($4::text[]))
                AND $5::numrange @> timestamp_ns
                ORDER BY timestamp_ns ASC
                LIMIT $6
